*Multiscreen Interface~ `<home>~

All sorts of campaign information can be displayed here. To change to
All sorts of campaign information can be displayed here. To change to
a different screen, enter the following command: "ms " followed by
the screen you wish to view. These are the currently available screens:

 `sceneinfo~ <id>       `editscene~ <id>
 `charinfo~ <id>        `editchar~ <id>
 `charlist~             `addchar~
 `scenelist~            `addscene~
 `log~
 `help~
 `find~ <term>
 `combat~
 `home~
 `changescene~ <id>
